力的根基？（25分）', '[]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:26:58+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "89ab12bb3bf9", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113040", "c": "304", "s": "0603", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "甲、申論題部分", "subject": "行政學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年公務人員特種考試關務人員考試、身心障礙人員考試、國軍上校以上軍官轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": "二", "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "colonel", "civil_category": "一般行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('colonel-7fec267e-moex-00057', 'colonel-7fec267e', 'colonel-7fec267e-moex-113-3a7b2121', 'sub-colonel-7fec267e-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '對於「行政」意涵不同切入觀點之敘述，下列何者正確？', '["政治的觀點認為「行政」探討行政院之作為即可", "管理的觀點關注於探討有效處理公務之方法和技術", "公共政策的觀點不探討政府選擇不作為之事項", "公共性的觀點主要源自於新公共管理論述之啟發"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:26:58+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "89ab12bb3bf9", "answer_pdf_sha1": "751e39132aa3", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113040", "c": "304", "s": "0603", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "行政學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年公務人員特種考試關務人員考試、身心障礙人員考試、國軍上校以上軍官轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 1, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "colonel", "civil_category": "一般行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('colonel-7fec267e-moex-00058', 'colonel-7fec267e', 'colonel-7fec267e-moex-113-3a7b2121', 'sub-colonel-7fec267e-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '對於公共治理之敘述，何者最為適當？', '["提倡公私協力和公民參與", "主張政治與行政二分", "強調層級節制與威權體系", "重視組織內部的行政程序 30460"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:26:58+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "89ab12bb3bf9", "answer_pdf_sha1": "751e39132aa3", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113040", "c": "304", "s": "0603", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "行政學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年公務人員特種考試關務人員考試、身心障礙人員考試、國軍上校以上軍官轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 2, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "colonel", "civil_category": "一般行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('colonel-7fec267e-moex-00059', 'colonel-7fec267e', 'colonel-7fec267e-moex-113-3a7b2121', 'sub-colonel-7fec267e-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關解除管制（de-regulation）的核心內涵，下列何者錯誤？', '["除去國家介入私營事業的所有管制手段", "減少進入市場之障礙與廢止不合市場機能之法律規範", "取消或減少對私經濟活動產生干預之行為", "國家對經濟行政管理強度的減低或方式調整"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:26:58+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "89ab12bb3bf9", "answer_pdf_sha1": "751e39132aa3", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113040", "c": "304", "s": "0603", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "行政學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年公務人員特種考試關務人員考試、身心障礙人員考試、國軍上校以上軍官轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 3, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "colonel", "civil_category": "一般行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('colonel-7fec267e-moex-00060', 'colonel-7fec267e', 'colonel-7fec267e-moex-113-3a7b2121', 'sub-colonel-7fec267e-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '羅聖朋和克拉夫丘克（D.H.Rosenbloom&R.S.Kravchuk）認為文官為主權 受託者，下列何者不屬於主權受託者應有的作為？', '["文官負責公共政策的制定與執行", "文官應動員政治支持為其政策倡議及辯護", "文官的決策應能符合商業團體的主要價值", "文官需具備旺盛的企圖心和長遠的眼光，以肆應未來的變遷"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:26:58+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "89ab12bb3bf9", "answer_pdf_sha1": "751e39132aa3", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113040", "c": "304", "s": "0603", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "行政學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年公務人員特種考試關務人員考試、身心障礙人員考試、國軍上校以上軍官轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 4, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "colonel", "civil_category": "一般行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('colonel-7fec267e-moex-00061', 'colonel-7fec267e', 'colonel-7fec267e-moex-113-3a7b2121', 'sub-colonel-7fec267e-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '以道德本身、道德判斷及道德原則作為研究對象的倫理研究，稱之為：', '["後設倫理學（metaethics）", "專業倫理學（professionalethics）", "法律倫理學（legalethics）", "行政倫理學（administrativeethics）"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:26:58+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "89ab12bb3bf9", "answer_pdf_sha1": "751e39132aa3", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113040", "c": "304", "s": "0603", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "行政學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年公務人員特種考試關務人員考試、身心障礙人員考試、國軍上校以上軍官轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 5, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "colonel", "civil_category": "一般行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
